ong>%d </strong>个单元在<strong>%d </strong>更新中进行了更改。</p><p><a href="%s" class="thickbox" title="搜索/替换详细信息">单击此处</a>以获取更多详细信息。</p>','(%s MB)'=>'(%s MB)','<p><strong>DRY RUN:</strong> <strong>%d</strong> tables were searched, <strong>%d</strong> cells were found that need to be updated, and <strong>%d</strong> changes were made.</p><p><a href="%s" class="thickbox" title="Dry Run Details">Click here</a> for more details, or use the form below to run the search/replace.</p>'=>'<p><strong> 模拟运行：</strong>：搜索了<strong>%d</strong>个表，找到了需要更新的<strong>%d </strong>行，以及<strong>%d个</strong>进行了更改。</p><p><a href="%s" class="thickbox" title="模拟运行详情">单击此处</a>以获得更多详细信息，或使用表单在下面运行搜索/替换。</p>','Table'=>'表','Time'=>'时间','Search for'=>'搜索','Rows Updated'=>'行已更新','If left unchecked, all database columns titled \'guid\' will be skipped.'=>'如果未选中，则将跳过所有标题为 \'guid\' 的数据库列。','Changes Found'=>'变更数量']];